[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.239,
    "text": "Hi! I'm Phil from BBC Learning English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.24,
    "endTime": 5.04,
    "text": "Today, I'm going to tell you the difference between"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.04,
    "endTime": 9.5,
    "text": "'affect' with an 'a' and 'effect' with an 'e'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.5,
    "endTime": 14.120000000000001,
    "text": "Just remember that 'affect' with an 'a' is a verb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.12,
    "endTime": 16.48,
    "text": "It means 'to influence'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.48,
    "endTime": 18.240000000000002,
    "text": "So, for example:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.5,
    "endTime": 23.240000000000002,
    "text": "Tiredness is affecting my work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.249,
    "endTime": 27.74,
    "text": "'Effect' with an 'e' is usually a noun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.74,
    "endTime": 30.259,
    "text": "and it means 'the result of something'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.26,
    "endTime": 32.72,
    "text": "The effect of not having breakfast is to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.72,
    "endTime": 34.22,
    "text": "feel really hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.22,
    "endTime": 36.019,
    "text": "'Effect' can be a verb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.02,
    "endTime": 39.300000000000004,
    "text": "It's very formal and it means 'to implement something'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.3,
    "endTime": 42.55,
    "text": "The management effected a new policy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.55,
    "endTime": 46.379,
    "text": "So if you find this difference affecting your English,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.38,
    "endTime": 50.620000000000005,
    "text": "just remember that 'affect' with an 'a' is a verb"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.62,
    "endTime": 54.16,
    "text": "and that 'effect' with an 'e' is usually a noun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.16,
    "endTime": 55.919,
    "text": "And the effect will be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.92,
    "endTime": 57.58,
    "text": "you don't make any more mistakes!"
  }
]